byline.original: As told to CATHERINE SAINT LOUIS

abstract: Dr Eleni Michailidis describes experience she and her husband went through when their son Alexander was stillborn.
lead_paragraph: After Dr. Eleni Michailidis delivered a stillborn son, she and her husband sought to honor their infant and the experience.

headline.main: After a Stillbirth, a Silent Delivery Room
